Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Hi, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Pedraum Pardehpoosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I run Product for the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for joining us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We've brought a few people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,together that normally don't get
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is going to be a session
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that might be a little different
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,than what you're used to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a deeper look into the App
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm thrilled that you joined
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard about the App Store
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,from Phil on Monday at the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,keynote.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the staggering numbers that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,demonstrate what a smash hit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But today we're going to spend a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,little time giving you an
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,overview of the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go a little deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll look at the design
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophy that went into the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"why" we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll go a little deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,into our emphasis on editorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, we'll bring it all back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and talk about the implications
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to you, the developers that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,bring it to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who remembers this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Cheering and Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the original App Store, the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,OG.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It had been launched in July of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,2008 with 500 apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a little inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There were some prominent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,executives at the company that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't think we'd have more than
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a thousand apps in the App Store
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The structure and the layout of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the store have largely remained
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We changed things here and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there, but overall it's the same
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tweaks have been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nine years later there are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,2.2 million apps in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:01:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's transformed the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,software is bought and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,distributed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to imagine a time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,before Apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's permeated every facet of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,our lives from the way we travel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to the way we find love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And they've affected entire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,industries as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,From airline travel to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,healthcare to gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as the way we play
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw this scene of people in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong Kong playing Pokemon Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think it's just bonkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well at this point in the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,history of the App Store, we
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,pause to consider how we can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,make it even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How we could redesign it from
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the ground up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we began doing that, we
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,realized it could serve a few
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One, we thought how can we give
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,customers a reason to come back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a destination they'd
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,want to visit on a daily basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, we thought this was a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,perfect time to double down on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the editorial curation that's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,distinguished the App Store
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,since its inception.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, we wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,reflect the significance the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,games play in the App Store and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,give both games and apps a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,clearer focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At this stage, we began an
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,intense journey of redesigning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the store from the ground up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you more about the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,process, I'm thrilled to hand it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,over to Monika Gromek who led
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,these design efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Monika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thanks Pedraum, for letting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,me out of the office once in a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you all for coming to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,this session.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Monika Gromek and I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,lead the App Store design team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This redesign of the App Store
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is so significant that we felt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it deserved a session dedicated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,just to this one topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And hopefully by the end of it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be much more familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with the changes that we're
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,making and all the new features
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're introducing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to cover the major
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,parts of the redesign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would like start with our
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,goals and the design process.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As Pedraum mentioned, the App
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Store launched nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's so hard to believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so much time has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are incredibly proud of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what it has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And mostly, thanks to all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the amazing apps and games
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that you create every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So why the redesign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was time for us to take
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a long, hard look at the current
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,store and acknowledge its
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,limitations, as none of us could
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,have predicted its tremendous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So just like every other app and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,game creator on the App Store,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we asked ourselves two
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,questions: What are our goals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does the current design
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,support them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For the new store, we touched
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,every single view and thought
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,hard about the structure of the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, there were a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,options on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We applied lessons from other
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,redesigns at Apple, but the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,final design is unique to the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The end result is a new sense of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,clarity, a general
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,simplification of the app, and a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,fresh take on editorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The new style of typography
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,helps establish hierarchy on the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,pages and a sense of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It guides people throughout
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,their journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also removed extra layers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of UIs such as toggles to help
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with the overall experience in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at our
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,redesign goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, these are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the same as the ones you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,heard a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This alignment of goals helped
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,us create a product that's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,integrated, fluid and also
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We did add one goal from the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,design side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is clarity and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,simplification.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's probably the most
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,important goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will expand on it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to start by talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the App Store as a daily
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,destination and the editorial
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,voice on the App Store, as the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,two goals are very closely
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,related.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that, I want to bring up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the Today view.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it in the Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,keynote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It all starts with the Today
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our new home for the App
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we can share our
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,passion for apps and games and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,celebrate all of you, the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,creators.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you can come and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,learn our editorial perspective
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,on the world of apps and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This view is a dynamic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ever-changing platform that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,allows us to feature your
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,products in a very different
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,light than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We designed it as a series of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,cards that update daily and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,allow us to celebrate your apps
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and games by telling stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had this desire to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,stories for a long time now but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't been able to do it in a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,meaningful and engaging way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is all changing now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Today tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What you see here is our video
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can highlight your app and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,game previews and our
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,editorially-created videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be providing helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,tips and tricks as seen in this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,example for VSCO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And we will be nominating an App
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Day and a Game of the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And we will also be sharing our
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,curated collections.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you might be familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,with our collections, as we've
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,been creating them for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but haven't had a way to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,highlight them in a predictable
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,way in our UI.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But again, this is different now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Today tab and these
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent a lot of time thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,about how to best showcase your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,apps and games in this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was important to us that it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,looked beautiful, so we spent a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,lot of time thinking about every
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,single detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything kept us up at night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for months, be it typography,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,layout, transitions and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,animations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Each card is an entry point for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a deeper discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And we also hope to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,some context into why you should
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,tap in and check out that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At any given point we will give
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you up to seven days' worth of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,content.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you miss a day or two, you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,can come back and find it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look for the date markers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We also included animations on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,some of these cards to make them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already seen the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,auto-playing video.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But we hope to bring more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,movement into this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve cards will be ready for
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We needed a variety to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,things interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But also to be able to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,diverse type of stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And each one of these cards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,allows us to tell a story in a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also important that these
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,cards look good together and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,work as a system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The order in which they appear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,might be different, so what you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,see one day might be very
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,different from what you will see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But, there's a lot of thought
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes into creating these
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,every single day around the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And believe me, it keeps things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting, even at Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I do want to share one other
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,thing about the cards, which is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,personally important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That this view is relevant world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So all this content will be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,localized and culturally aware
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in all our territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a closer look at one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of these stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It focuses on the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,behind every app there is a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,story of who made it, what
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,motivated them, and how it was
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It celebrates you and your apps
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The transition into this story
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is smooth and fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's also easy to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,out to the Today view.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply tap on the X button or
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,swipe down on the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The stories are engaging and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,informative.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Smokey, who leads our editorial
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,team, will come on stage in a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,bit and talk to you about it in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,more detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to highlight a few
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,elements of these stories from
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the design perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're letting the elements of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the stories define the space,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing them to breathe and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,convey our perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The videos let us engage with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the viewer like we've never been
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,able to do before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And each story is a series of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,modules defined by our design
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and editorial teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We also hope that you will share
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,these stories with one another
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and enjoy them as much as we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The modules allow for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,flexibility in terms of how
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,these stories are built.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But they also keep things
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,consistent from the design side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have this common language
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that ties them all together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,making it easier for people to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,experience that content.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also worth mentioning that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first time ever this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,editorial content will be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,searchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've actually never had that in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are incredibly excited
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you miss a day, or if you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,miss some of this content, be it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Today tab or any other
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,place in the App Store, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,simply search for it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be featured on the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,product page as well for that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,app or game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the Today tab
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,will be part of this App Store
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,on the iPad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the Today view.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're incredibly excited about
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how it looks and how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, about the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,type of stories it will allow us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell you every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about games next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Games have been always a huge
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,part of the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But up to this point always
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,mixed with apps throughout our
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,editorial and charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of their importance and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,success, we're dedicating a home
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,just for games in the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the new Games tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It is more than a tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're striving to create the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,best, world's best game store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Full of amazing content that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,people are going to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The top of the page allows for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,space for more stories to be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,dedicated just to games or new
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,releases.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And with more focus on videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,people will be able to discover
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,games much more quickly and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,engage with them almost
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The split between apps and games
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also allowed us to make charts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,much more relevant in the App
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the charts that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing are specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,dedicated to games.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the same is true for apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They will not be mixed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We think this will actually make
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it a lot easier to find what's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,popular on the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The same is true of categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As some of you may know, games
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,was just one of the categories
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the previous store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, what it meant is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that all the subcategories were
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,harder to find and all that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,content was hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But creating a tab dedicated for
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,games, we can take all those
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,categories and put them on the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,top level, making browsing by
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,categories a lot easier and that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,content a lot easier to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout the App Store will
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,also be providing more context
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for any particular app or game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The App Store is no longer just
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,app icons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to help people find what
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,they're looking for and make the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,right download choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The context can come from your
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,subtitles that you will be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,providing for your apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And these subtitles are as
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,important as your app names
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And again, it's to provide
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,people with more information
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,about your app and game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The context can also come from
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the editorial team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will see more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of it throughout the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the new Games tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're incredibly excited about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,having a dedicated home for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we move on, I just wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to highlight a small but playful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,detail about the Games tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Icon. The shape of the rocket is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,actually based on the leaf from
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the Apple logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought some of you might
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,find it interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to the Games tab,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we're also creating a new home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All the amazing content that you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,saw for the Games tab will also
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,be available in the Apps tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,From the design perspective
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,there was always this tension
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,between apps and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And we felt it was a problem we
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,needed to solve, as apps are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,incredibly important and have a
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,huge impact on how we live our
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By splitting games and apps we
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,can give both of them the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,attention they deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And finding new apps will be so
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,much easier with App Previews,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as you see in this example for
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mammals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What you will see in both tabs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are in-app purchases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to this point they had a very
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,limited presence in the App
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're changing it completely
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with this redesign.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be much more
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,accessible and discoverable
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You will see them on the Today
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We actually designed a card
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,specifically for in-app
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,purchases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be highlighted on the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps and Games tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And they will be searchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They will also be featured by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you on your product pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a complete story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's probably even more
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,important, how easy it is to get
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the in-app purchases, especially
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,if you have the app installed on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,your own device.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to start with the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Today tab and the card
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,specifically designed for the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in-app purchases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tap on the Buy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,button.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The app will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the purchase sheet will come
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can confirm with Touch ID and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple and direct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When designing the visual
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,treatment for in-app purchases,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it was important to us that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,these wouldn't be confused for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,being app icons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We started with the image that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be providing for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,featuring your in-app purchases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And we added a framing system
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that helps convey what these
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,truly are, in addition to an app
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the [inaudible] helps
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,communicate that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The curve of the frame actually
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,follows the shape of the app
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,icons on the App Store today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way we think of in-app
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,purchases is that they are the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,smaller part of the larger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,piece, which is the app itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also still important to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,us to keep that connection
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,between the in-app purchase and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the parent app.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So we added the app icon in the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,lower left corner, again for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,more context.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would like to feature
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,your in-app purchases on a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,store, you will need to submit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,an image for every single one of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,your in-app purchases.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs to be a custom design
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,asset that helps describe what
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,your in-app purchase is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It should not be a screen shot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,from your app or an app icon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The last goal, clarity and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,simplification, is also the most
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,important, like I mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier, from the design
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It also had the biggest
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,influence on the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,redesign.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When designing our products, we
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly ask ourselves: Is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,this simple enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this clear to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And can we achieve the same goal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with less?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The most significant area of the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store that probably
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,demonstrates how this goal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,affected our process is the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Product page.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also home for your apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to spend a little more
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,time on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the years, we've added a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,lot of different features to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this page without having the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunity to take a step back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and look at it holistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew we had to simplify,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,especially the top of the page,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as this is what your customers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,see first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of the relevant
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,information had to be clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,communicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to highlight this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,app's achievement on the App
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So its star rating, Editor's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Choice and charting position, if
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,available.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We included age rating to this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,section, as we know it's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,incredibly important, especially
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for those of us who are parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All this information had to be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly scannable and easy to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Videos and screenshots are still
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the heroes of this page, just
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,like they are today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But now with auto-playing video,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,this page comes to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You will also get up to three
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,videos versus just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know that people want to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,engage with beautiful app
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,previews.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we will feature them much
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,more heavily throughout our UI.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We redesigned how we communicate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,if this app is universal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also how you see screen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,shots from the other devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We enjoy apps that have been
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,designed and work on all the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,different devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We drastically simplified how we
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,present ratings and reviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're much easier to read, and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,their presentation has -- their
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,graphic presentation has been
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've removed the All versions
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,versus Current version split
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,between ratings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So updating your apps will no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,longer hide your ratings the way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it does today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The reviews are really easy to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply swipe to the left or tap
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,on the CL link.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we included the Editor's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Choice in this section as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the reviews are in one
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The information section
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,underwent a makeover as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:22:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a lot easier to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are featuring more apps
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and games by this developer on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,this page or any other products
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that are related and you might
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lastly, it was important to us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to make it easy for you as you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,scroll down the page to download
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the app.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We love the bar that comes down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,as you absorb the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The transition is smooth and the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,bar is integrated with the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,overall page design.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the redesigned App
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked hard to make the new
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,store a place people will love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and will want to come to every
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And we hope you agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I want to invite Smokey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fontaine to talk to you about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.73,0:22:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,our editorial strategy for the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,new App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for your
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you, Monika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Monika, so much for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:22:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,showing us that beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful redesign.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Smokey Fontaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And yes, that is my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In many ways I'm glad they don't
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,let me touch the product.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.81,0:23:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I only get to touch the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,editorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the editorial director here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my great pleasure to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,really talk to us about what
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,does "editorial" mean for the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How does original content, how
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.03,0:23:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,will it bring our customers to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the store in new and exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And how can our added
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,perspective really transform the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,store from the phenomenal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,service and utility it has
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,always been to a place where our
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,users and our customers can come
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,back and read, watch, and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.97,0:23:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,listen, and discover more than
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,they ever, ever have before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what we're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our editorial principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the set of new tabs, as
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you've seen today, games and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,More options for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll end with the big
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the Editorial Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first and foremost, we are
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We are fans of all of the work
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We really, really love this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm standing here right
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.38,0:24:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,now without my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm feeling a little lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How many folks have actually
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,used an app since this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.70,0:24:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,presentation has been on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone? How many people have
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,played a game since this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,presentation has been on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone? Well, maybe you're even
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,making, you're finishing your
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.50,0:24:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,apps and polishing up your games
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.73,0:24:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what we love to do as
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.51,0:24:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.10,0:24:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, all of our App Store
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.60,0:24:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,editors around the world wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.19,0:24:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,really excited to try to find
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.32,0:24:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that innovative new app that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,could change someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.34,0:24:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Or that exciting game that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.01,0:24:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,customers will spend hours and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.40,0:24:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,hours and hours playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We care deeply about all the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,recommendations we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.99,0:24:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We play every game we recommend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.98,0:24:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And we use every app that we
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.00,0:24:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,recommend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The redesign is so exciting for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.61,0:24:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,us because now we have the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.36,0:24:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,ability to provide even more
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.87,0:25:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,context, even more perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.53,0:25:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and in many ways a narrative to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.32,0:25:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,our recommendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.55,0:25:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So customers can come and find
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.96,0:25:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,everything they want and need
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.45,0:25:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Find all of the work that you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.31,0:25:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,create.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.75,0:25:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a set of editorial
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.63,0:25:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.80,0:25:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you come to our story
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.26,0:25:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,rooms around the world, and this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.30,0:25:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is not just in Cupertino, but
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.97,0:25:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,this is in London and Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.73,0:25:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is in Seoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.75,0:25:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is even in Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.87,0:25:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,These editorial principles
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.65,0:25:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,really guide the writing that we
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.68,0:25:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,will write.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.47,0:25:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They will guide our creative
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.47,0:25:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,process.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.43,0:25:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We start with the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.58,0:25:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We celebrate apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.28,0:25:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This for us is really our most
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.69,0:25:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,important point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.76,0:25:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we have a bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.81,0:25:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,editorial platform, it does not
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.34,0:25:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,mean that we're going to all of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.48,0:25:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a sudden start reviewing apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.84,0:25:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not mean that we're
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.10,0:25:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,going to all of a sudden going
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.10,0:25:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to start criticizing apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.78,0:25:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We are cheer leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.97,0:25:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Unapologetic cheerleaders of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.20,0:25:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,apps and app culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:25:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For us, it's really the most
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.95,0:25:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,creative work in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.64,0:25:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is our number one
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.71,0:25:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.21,0:26:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We celebrate apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.24,0:26:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Second is that we are the voice
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.95,0:26:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.12,0:26:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, during this redesign
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.22,0:26:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we thought long and hard about
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.88,0:26:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,not only what we're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,write, but how we're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.68,0:26:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.78,0:26:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big responsibility to be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.23,0:26:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.90,0:26:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big responsibility to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.09,0:26:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of be the mouthpiece to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.71,0:26:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,hundreds and hundreds of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.73,0:26:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,millions of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.24,0:26:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that we want to kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.60,0:26:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,be authentic to who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.28,0:26:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We want it to be smart and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.97,0:26:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We want it to be humble, for
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.45,0:26:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.98,0:26:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And very friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.13,0:26:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, a lot of our work
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.26,0:26:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,will be in a kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,conversational tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.78,0:26:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, we want to be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.15,0:26:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,passionate about all the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.10,0:26:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to be very Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to obsess over every
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.57,0:26:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,word, every word, every word, so
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.71,0:26:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that our customers can -- we can
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.97,0:26:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,help them and engage them as
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.75,0:26:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,best as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.26,0:26:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's our third principle?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.41,0:26:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we offer independent
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.16,0:26:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,insights.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.12,0:26:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's one of the biggest
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.00,0:26:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,criticisms of the App Store?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.26,0:26:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that it's all paid
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.36,0:26:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,marketing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.64,0:26:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of you in this room may
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.89,0:26:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have tried to engage us with
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.77,0:26:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,suggestions to feature one of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.98,0:27:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,your apps or feature one of your
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.22,0:27:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,games.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.70,0:27:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you probably know that money
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.90,0:27:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.34,0:27:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing in the redesigned
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.19,0:27:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store on Today Games or Apps
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.82,0:27:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.07,0:27:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are strong experts with an
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.09,0:27:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,editorial point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.74,0:27:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are great storytellers
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.31,0:27:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,with a personality and with a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.84,0:27:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,perspective that we want to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.35,0:27:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,share.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.70,0:27:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why is this important?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.82,0:27:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We want customers to really
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.07,0:27:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,trust the recommendations that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.53,0:27:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.50,0:27:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We want them to be able to rely
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.88,0:27:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,on what we share with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.37,0:27:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? So they'll ultimately come
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.06,0:27:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,back every day and find
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.17,0:27:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,tremendous value in the App
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.72,0:27:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Store's editorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.08,0:27:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth. While we wordsmith this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.86,0:27:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot, let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.60,0:27:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We tell interesting and
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.73,0:27:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,important stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.56,0:27:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,First it was, "We tell
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.49,0:27:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting stories."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.89,0:27:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it was, "We tell insanely
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.93,0:27:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting stories."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.20,0:27:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is where we landed,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.42,0:27:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Interesting and important
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.99,0:27:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,stories."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.36,0:27:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for sure, not every single
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.48,0:27:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,story on Today is going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.49,0:27:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,super, super important.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.06,0:27:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're going to try really,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.16,0:27:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,really hard to make sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.46,0:27:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,they are very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.32,0:28:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They key for us is that us being
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.47,0:28:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,able to say that this app is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.64,0:28:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,great is no longer enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.00,0:28:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In the current app store, that's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.71,0:28:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.60,0:28:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And we feature and promote those
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.21,0:28:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.91,0:28:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In our new design, newly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.49,0:28:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,designed App Store, we will say
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.90,0:28:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that app is great, but then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.15,0:28:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,explain why we believe it is to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.79,0:28:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.88,0:28:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to provide
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.74,0:28:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,thought-provoking ideas and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.40,0:28:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,really offer that context.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.96,0:28:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fifth and last principle is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.22,0:28:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we deliver a fresh and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.97,0:28:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,unexpected take.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.02,0:28:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the world of apps is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.33,0:28:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,moving at a ridiculous speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.41,0:28:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is our job, we believe, to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.86,0:28:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,reflect that innovative culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.61,0:28:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are pushing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.88,0:28:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.54,0:28:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you are shaping our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.44,0:28:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with what you create.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.16,0:28:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And often you've changed things
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.09,0:28:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in ways that are totally
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.20,0:28:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.88,0:28:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we want to try to keep up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.27,0:28:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up with that speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.83,0:28:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And for us, we kind of call this
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.09,0:28:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,our "the crazy ones" principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.28,0:28:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A fresh and unexpected take.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.41,0:28:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So these five principles all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.91,0:28:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,together: We celebrate apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.33,0:29:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the voice of the App
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.64,0:29:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.50,0:29:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We offer independent insights.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.01,0:29:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We tell interesting and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.98,0:29:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,important stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.17,0:29:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And we deliver a fresh and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.31,0:29:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,unexpected take.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.39,0:29:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When we do all this, if around
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.79,0:29:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the world we abide by these
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.55,0:29:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,principles, then hopefully the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.44,0:29:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today tab and the whole new App
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.07,0:29:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Store become a pretty fabulous
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.94,0:29:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,document of app culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.83,0:29:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And for us at the App Store, app
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.28,0:29:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,culture in almost every single
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.72,0:29:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,way is culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.46,0:29:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.27,0:29:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The new tabs: Today, Games, and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.67,0:29:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.43,0:29:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of these tabs have the same
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.81,0:29:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.48,0:29:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we approach them
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.32,0:29:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.06,0:29:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, well, Today is going to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.47,0:29:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,be updated every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.64,0:29:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't really have a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.56,0:29:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.87,0:29:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.49,0:29:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to have a very
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.42,0:29:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,focused perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.54,0:29:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be highly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.19,0:29:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,contextual.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.60,0:29:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And when customers tap on cards
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.33,0:29:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in Today, they can actually go
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.10,0:29:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,directly to buy that app or game
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.44,0:29:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.38,0:29:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or of course, tap in and read
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.07,0:29:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,one of our stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.94,0:29:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Games and Apps tabs are
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.11,0:29:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.13,0:30:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In many ways you can think about
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.44,0:30:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,those as a 2.0 version or a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.08,0:30:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,newly evolved version of the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.41,0:30:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Feature tab now, including
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.49,0:30:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,categories and including charts,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.17,0:30:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as you're seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.10,0:30:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Games and Apps tabs
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.19,0:30:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,are going to be updated often.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.64,0:30:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.96,0:30:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But more often than the weekly
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.39,0:30:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that you see in today's cadence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.65,0:30:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Games and Apps are going to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.42,0:30:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,offer a broader selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.08,0:30:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's generally going to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.39,0:30:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,more transactional experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.01,0:30:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Taps on Games and Apps will take
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.97,0:30:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,customers directly to our
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.75,0:30:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,amazing new product pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.58,0:30:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me chat a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.74,0:30:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,about what we call our Story
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.60,0:30:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Framework.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.26,0:30:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're seeing, stories on the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.00,0:30:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store will cover many, many
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.44,0:30:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.09,0:30:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have world premieres.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.22,0:30:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have major updates.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.42,0:30:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have tips and tricks and
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,interviews with developers and
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.03,0:30:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,lists upon lists.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.45,0:30:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, our job is to write about
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.08,0:30:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what we think customers will
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.06,0:30:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,find most interesting about an
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.92,0:30:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,app or a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.47,0:30:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And we really believe every app
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.87,0:30:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,has a story to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.39,0:30:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are four main topics of
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.63,0:30:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,stories for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.18,0:30:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When we think about all the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.26,0:30:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,range, the broad, broad range of
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.81,0:31:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,ideas that we have, we try to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.37,0:31:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,make -- we needed to make sense
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.43,0:31:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.74,0:31:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So we started with just an idea
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.09,0:31:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of topics.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.95,0:31:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the four main topics
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.58,0:31:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that we will cover?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.75,0:31:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And for each topic we kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.39,0:31:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,have a statement of belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.03,0:31:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something that we really
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.79,0:31:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,want to have customers feel in
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.25,0:31:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the writing and the content that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.46,0:31:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we create.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.05,0:31:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first topic is, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.91,0:31:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.75,0:31:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a big name game or
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.32,0:31:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a small indie who has a
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.38,0:31:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,car-based strategy, RPG,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.86,0:31:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite Runner, it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.62,0:31:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.87,0:31:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The games you make are so
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.98,0:31:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,innovative and so creative, our
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.64,0:31:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,game editors really believe
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.92,0:31:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.35,0:31:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps are the future of gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.73,0:31:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In many ways apps are the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.50,0:31:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,present of gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.73,0:31:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone agree with that comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.09,0:31:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps are the present of gaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.88,0:31:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we do have the biggest
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.82,0:31:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,gaming platform in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.13,0:31:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know, we're very
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.11,0:31:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiastic about expressing to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.23,0:31:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,our customers what we believe
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.74,0:31:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the future is in games.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.43,0:31:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Our second topic: Lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.02,0:31:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do we believe there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.04,0:31:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps transform your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.56,0:31:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's social networking
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.73,0:31:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,or photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.52,0:31:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's dating or fitness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.69,0:31:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or cooking or transportation,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.92,0:32:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,apps have helped us live in ways
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.14,0:32:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've never, ever, ever
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.21,0:32:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,thought possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.14,0:32:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And we believe in our lifestyle
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.64,0:32:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,coverage that apps transform
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.59,0:32:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.07,0:32:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Third, culture and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.94,0:32:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.43,0:32:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps shape culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.80,0:32:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is music, film,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.03,0:32:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.58,0:32:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is TV, pop culture and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.37,0:32:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.26,0:32:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The App Store is going to bring
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.43,0:32:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,all that together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.99,0:32:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And so App Store [inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.28,0:32:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,content may talk to celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.58,0:32:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We may talk to influencers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.20,0:32:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We may talk to culture creators
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.74,0:32:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of all kinds about the world of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.29,0:32:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,apps and games because we
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.81,0:32:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,believe apps really do shape
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.63,0:32:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.79,0:32:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And our fourth and final topic
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.36,0:32:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is, of course, new tech and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.17,0:32:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,innovation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.77,0:32:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all things new, new,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.10,0:32:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,new.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.75,0:32:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,New services.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.55,0:32:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,New ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.33,0:32:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,New capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.67,0:32:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely new ways of getting
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.93,0:32:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,things done with your iPhone or
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.34,0:32:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,iPad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.11,0:32:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And we really feel that we can
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.52,0:32:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,provide a service to customers
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.25,0:32:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to help them figure it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.30,0:32:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Help them get great use out of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.56,0:32:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all the innovative work that you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.86,0:32:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.51,0:32:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And help them potentially be
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.84,0:32:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,introduced into a whole new way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.42,0:32:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.61,0:33:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In many ways it's very Apple of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.03,0:33:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.29,0:33:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to make the complex
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.48,0:33:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,world of technology simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.42,0:33:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.07,0:33:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Four topics: Gaming, lifestyle,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.58,0:33:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,culture and entertainment, and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.74,0:33:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,new tech and innovation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.26,0:33:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When we take these topics, and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.55,0:33:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,once we've decided on one, then
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.46,0:33:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we want to apply what we call an
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.06,0:33:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"intention."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.84,0:33:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is essentially the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.73,0:33:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,purpose or the goal of each
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.29,0:33:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,story that you will see on the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.97,0:33:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.44,0:33:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There are three of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.75,0:33:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The first we call "Inform."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.64,0:33:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about being timely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.36,0:33:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about giving customers
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.62,0:33:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"need-to-know" information.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.25,0:33:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to obviously let them
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.68,0:33:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,know what's happening in the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.74,0:33:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,world right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.32,0:33:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, you can say a new
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.12,0:33:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,show is launching on Netflix.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.83,0:33:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we do that well, our
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.93,0:33:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,customer reaction may very
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.19,0:33:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,likely be: "Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.64,0:33:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get that."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.75,0:33:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our second intention is simply
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.31,0:33:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,called "Help."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.44,0:33:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really important for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.67,0:33:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about being
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.40,0:33:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,instructional.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.10,0:33:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about being
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.81,0:33:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,motivational.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.93,0:33:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about sharing ideas that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.47,0:33:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,may be intuitive for us but not
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.56,0:33:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.56,0:33:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How to get the most out of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.52,0:33:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Instagram's new feature could be
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.32,0:33:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,a helpful topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.82,0:34:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And for us, this can be a really
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.89,0:34:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,helpful way of reengaging our
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.13,0:34:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,customers with some apps that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.35,0:34:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,they may have downloaded, may
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.99,0:34:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,knew they loved them, but
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.75,0:34:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,they've been left idle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.08,0:34:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can we reengage our
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.36,0:34:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,customers with some of those
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.55,0:34:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,apps and even games by helping
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.56,0:34:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,them, giving them new ideas of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.15,0:34:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,how to use one of these great
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.12,0:34:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,things?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.64,0:34:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And third, it's "Inspire."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.71,0:34:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be the topic
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.01,0:34:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,area or the intention where we
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.89,0:34:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,have really creative content,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.82,0:34:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,really motivational content,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.23,0:34:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,really insightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.99,0:34:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be everything
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.82,0:34:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,from a twelve-year-old making an
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.98,0:34:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,app to the 82-year-old making an
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.61,0:34:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,app, both of whom were here this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.81,0:34:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.45,0:34:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is inspiring content that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.53,0:34:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,may go global around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.40,0:34:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Inform, help and inspire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.87,0:34:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we inform, "Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.47,0:34:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get that."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.42,0:34:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we help, "I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.24,0:34:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks." And if we inspire,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.00,0:34:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.86,0:34:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's super interesting."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.88,0:34:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, we are not going
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.05,0:34:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to count any of those reactions
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.41,0:34:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,unless customers use those exact
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.25,0:34:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,phrases on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.09,0:34:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how this all comes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.78,0:35:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.09,0:35:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.78,0:35:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first world premiere ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.41,0:35:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,ever, ever is "The Art of the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.93,0:35:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.99,0:35:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the extraordinary world
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.11,0:35:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of Monument Valley 2."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.38,0:35:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why did we choose this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.47,0:35:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,First and foremost, it comes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.61,0:35:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,back to our first principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.95,0:35:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which was Monument Valley 2 is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.48,0:35:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,an awesome, awesome game.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.84,0:35:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How many folks have tried it so
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.03,0:35:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,far?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.97,0:35:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Monday release.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.08,0:35:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say I have not even got
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.48,0:35:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,very far.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.50,0:35:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a phenomenal,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.85,0:35:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomenal game.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.18,0:35:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ustwo did a great job with
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.06,0:35:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.23,0:35:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So first and foremost, we chose
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.85,0:35:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Monument Valley 2 as our world
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.23,0:35:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,premiere because the game is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.84,0:35:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,flat our awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.25,0:35:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, the Ustwo team gave us
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.44,0:35:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,great access to their
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.95,0:35:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,development process.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.24,0:35:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They allowed us in and we got to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.44,0:35:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,meet with some of their
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.07,0:35:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,creatives and speak to some of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.26,0:35:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,their art directors about what
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.37,0:35:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,inspired them to make Monument
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.18,0:35:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Valley 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.09,0:35:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really interesting and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.41,0:35:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,exciting for us because we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.71,0:35:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we could tell that story, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.42,0:35:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.66,0:35:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And thirdly, we knew we had a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.25,0:35:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,great story for customers about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.87,0:35:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Monument Valley 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.20,0:35:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course it helped that it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.34,0:35:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,was only available on iOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.53,0:36:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.60,0:36:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a moment in the third
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.63,0:36:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,stage of Monument Valley 2 when
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.94,0:36:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a landslide separates mother
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.28,0:36:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,from child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.76,0:36:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually did get to this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.73,0:36:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,level.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.45,0:36:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To get her little one back, mom
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.88,0:36:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,must navigate through intricate,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.23,0:36:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,artfully-crafted puzzle that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.39,0:36:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly evolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.03,0:36:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an actual moment, I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.61,0:36:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,got to it later, but one of our
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.85,0:36:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,game editors, this really
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.38,0:36:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.97,0:36:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He was playing and it's like "Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.84,0:36:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.09,0:36:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was such an awesome moment."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.25,0:36:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they embrace after.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.23,0:36:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And it really kind of moved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.47,0:36:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And we said, "You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.67,0:36:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the intro to our Monument
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.41,0:36:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Valley 2 story."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.42,0:36:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen some of the beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.51,0:36:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.33,0:36:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen how the copy flows in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.01,0:36:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,between these great images and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.95,0:36:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in-line video.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.16,0:36:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, we have pull
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.17,0:36:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,quotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.63,0:36:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple didn't invent pull quotes,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.45,0:36:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's really nice to see them
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.27,0:36:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,on the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.56,0:36:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we quoted us to studio head
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.28,0:36:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dan Gray, who wants to change
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.96,0:36:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,people's perceptions of what
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.23,0:36:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,games can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.80,0:36:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our first world premiere
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.80,0:36:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of Monument Valley 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.84,0:36:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is our first How To column.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.41,0:36:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Monika spoke about a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.27,0:36:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.77,0:36:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.18,0:36:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many, many ways we
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.75,0:37:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,could have spoken about VSCO.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.02,0:37:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of our favorite apps
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.17,0:37:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of our favorite photo
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.15,0:37:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,filter apps for a long, long
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.60,0:37:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.58,0:37:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we wanted to -- we felt
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.43,0:37:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the most helpful angle would be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.11,0:37:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of a basic primer of some
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.06,0:37:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the new features of VSCO that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.36,0:37:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,many customers may not have used
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.87,0:37:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.84,0:37:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's look at some of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.39,0:37:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.69,0:37:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.40,0:37:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a good denim jacket -- it's
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.81,0:37:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,funny, we had this image.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.41,0:37:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was initially the phrase is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.02,0:37:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,often "like a good leather
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.18,0:37:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,jacket."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.94,0:37:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We changed it to "like a good
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.17,0:37:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,denim jacket."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.77,0:37:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people love the denim
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.87,0:37:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,jacket that we gave out WWDC
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.63,0:37:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Swag this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.95,0:37:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm glad, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.37,0:37:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Round of applause for the denim
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.55,0:37:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,jackets.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.02,0:37:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.52,0:37:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well here you are right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.56,0:37:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a good denim jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.16,0:37:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,VSCO's got a coolness factor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.56,0:37:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that can't be measured.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.47,0:37:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we wanted to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.37,0:37:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,about creating gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.55,0:37:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Many folks don't know that you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.31,0:37:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,can create gifts in VSCO.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.16,0:37:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a feature that many users,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.69,0:37:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,both amateur and pro, love to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.47,0:37:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.14,0:37:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.48,0:37:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We go now, we can make journals
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.99,0:37:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of VSCO.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.52,0:37:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We talk about some of their free
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.33,0:37:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,filters.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.18,0:38:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, we end here with
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.92,0:38:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind of hidden, if you will,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.62,0:38:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,social network that's within
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.93,0:38:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,VSCO.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.60,0:38:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tip number five, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.65,0:38:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,socialize without having to go
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.15,0:38:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.12,0:38:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was our first How To
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.10,0:38:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,story.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.20,0:38:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very interesting because
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.12,0:38:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the biggest challenges
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.55,0:38:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about App Store Editorial is how
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.76,0:38:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,can we serve a billion people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.10,0:38:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.69,0:38:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really, really, really
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.48,0:38:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.67,0:38:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,first who you want to speak to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.61,0:38:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's as important to us on
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.02,0:38:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the App Store to talk to new
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.19,0:38:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,users as it is to talk to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.78,0:38:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced users.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.64,0:38:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is column is more for an
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.20,0:38:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced user.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.36,0:38:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We call this a Deep Dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.80,0:38:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's it's a conversation about
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.33,0:38:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.41,0:38:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my game editors was
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.76,0:38:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,really excited when he got to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.20,0:38:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,level 201 because everything
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.12,0:38:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,changes on level 201.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.23,0:38:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to feel like a genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.49,0:38:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,well, you better get there
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.99,0:38:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,first.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.31,0:38:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was a story about a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.11,0:38:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,great game in a kind of deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.47,0:38:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,context.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.46,0:38:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We talk about culture and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.36,0:38:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,entertainment, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.38,0:39:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the NBA finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.36,0:39:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that game is on tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.68,0:39:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.79,0:39:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I better not say anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.24,0:39:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in San Jose, California.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.25,0:39:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.03,0:39:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you look at culture and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.42,0:39:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,entertainment through the lens
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.69,0:39:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of apps, there are two actual
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.70,0:39:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ways that you can enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.19,0:39:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you can watch the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.54,0:39:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,game live anywhere you are on
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.72,0:39:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ESPN.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.60,0:39:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can also play the game
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.25,0:39:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,on NBA Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.35,0:39:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can imitate Steph Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.76,0:39:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or LeBron or whoever you'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.04,0:39:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to be on the game itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.62,0:39:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In many ways the game is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.33,0:39:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,probably going to be as good as
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.93,0:39:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-- the video game is going to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.23,0:39:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,imitate the real-life game and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.16,0:39:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,back and forth, seeing how these
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.95,0:39:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,players are breaking all these
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.00,0:39:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,records these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.93,0:39:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's our culture and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.32,0:39:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,entertainment story.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.66,0:39:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of examples.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.89,0:39:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's one thing this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.09,0:39:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,morning I love all of you to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.42,0:39:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,leave here and remember about
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.29,0:39:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the all new App Store is that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.45,0:39:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there are more ways to be
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.44,0:39:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,featured than ever, ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.39,0:39:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about "Meet the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.38,0:39:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Developer."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.82,0:39:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.37,0:39:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get interviewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.14,0:39:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Our debut "Meet the Developer"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.32,0:39:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,piece featured Michelle Kennedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.36,0:39:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the creator of a wonderful new
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.58,0:40:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,social media app called Peanut,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.40,0:40:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which is dedicated to moms.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.13,0:40:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our "Meet the Developer"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.39,0:40:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,column.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.31,0:40:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked to her about many
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.25,0:40:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,things, about her UI and some of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.77,0:40:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the feature innovations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.02,0:40:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we talked to her about some
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.30,0:40:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of the feedback she's received
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.86,0:40:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from her Peanut social media app
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.17,0:40:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and who it's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.02,0:40:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're really excited to have
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.62,0:40:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a kind of deeper cultural
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.88,0:40:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation about an app that's
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.65,0:40:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,really meaningful to a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.05,0:40:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Peanut is human interaction in
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.03,0:40:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,real life, facilitated by
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.86,0:40:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,technology," Michelle said.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.47,0:40:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Another way you can get featured
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.46,0:40:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is, of course, App of the Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.88,0:40:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we chose Hit List.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.29,0:40:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Game of the Day, Super Senso.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.94,0:40:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Strategic sci-fi combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.66,0:40:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me pause for a second and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.64,0:40:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,talk about App of the Day and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.03,0:40:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Game of the Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.06,0:40:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have Editor's Choice
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.53,0:40:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.11,0:40:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, Editor's Choice is now
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.33,0:40:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a badge on our new product
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.01,0:40:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.59,0:40:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,App of the Day and Game of the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.79,0:40:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Day give us a third option of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.78,0:40:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,really honoring all the great
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.32,0:40:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,work you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.15,0:40:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of Editor's Choice like
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.35,0:40:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,our Oscars.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.54,0:40:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like our Best Picture, if you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.84,0:40:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,will.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.19,0:40:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,App of the Day and Game of the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.48,0:40:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Day are going to be similarly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.40,0:41:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,high quality, super awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.80,0:41:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,apps, but they'll also be pegged
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.77,0:41:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to a story that we may want to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.83,0:41:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.77,0:41:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Another way to be featured is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.82,0:41:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Collections.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.28,0:41:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Collections are going to be on
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.04,0:41:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the Games and Apps tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.50,0:41:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They are also going to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.05,0:41:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,on Today with a cool new design.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.84,0:41:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You will see here that Heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.26,0:41:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what we call Heroes on the Apps
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.14,0:41:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.49,0:41:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have AirBNB to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.10,0:41:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,rediscover this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.70,0:41:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have Injustice 2 as a new
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.55,0:41:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,game in the Games tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.30,0:41:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Another way to be featured is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.67,0:41:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,lists, lists and more lists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.66,0:41:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Our debut one is "15 Inspired
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.85,0:41:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Indie Games."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.81,0:41:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Customers irrespective of the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.34,0:41:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,media love lists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.30,0:41:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And we love them as well on the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.93,0:41:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.34,0:41:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.37,0:41:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings us to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.94,0:41:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The big, big question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.47,0:41:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you've enjoyed our kind
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.91,0:41:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of editorial vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.94,0:41:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a marriage of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.63,0:41:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,expert curation with this idea
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.40,0:41:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of engaging stories and content
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.44,0:41:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.40,0:41:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But really all we want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.62,0:41:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is this: How do you reach us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.51,0:42:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm happy to announce, and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.89,0:42:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,many of you, many have already
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.09,0:42:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.82,0:42:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm happy to announce that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.97,0:42:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,on AppStore.com/promote, that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.54,0:42:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,will redirect to the new
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.80,0:42:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Developer page where not only
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.70,0:42:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,will we ask you about your app
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.35,0:42:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and your game and the features
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.81,0:42:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and what's cool about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.71,0:42:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll also have a new area where
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.76,0:42:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it says, "Tell us your story."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.28,0:42:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really, really excited to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.89,0:42:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,hear all of the stories you have
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.76,0:42:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to share with us about your
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.26,0:42:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,creative process and what you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.87,0:42:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,want to share with your
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.56,0:42:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,customers about apps and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.76,0:42:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.06,0:42:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really excited to be on
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.54,0:42:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,this journey together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.11,0:42:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.18,0:42:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like now to bring back Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.08,0:42:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedraum Pardehpoosh to bring us
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.76,0:42:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,home.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.82,0:42:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thanks, Smokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.77,0:42:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you heard some insights into
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.34,0:42:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the why we did this redesign
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.33,0:42:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,from the lead designer herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.19,0:42:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a pretty special thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.23,0:42:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you heard the insights from
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.39,0:42:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Smokey about our doubling down
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.43,0:42:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,on editorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.85,0:42:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And got contact information for
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.54,0:43:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,how to get in touch with the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.67,0:43:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Editorial Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.40,0:43:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the dawn of a new day, I
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.73,0:43:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,think it's safe to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.15,0:43:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's not lose sight of the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.27,0:43:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,fact that ultimately all of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.12,0:43:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,these efforts are meant to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.50,0:43:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,improve the discoverability of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.83,0:43:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,apps and games on the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.79,0:43:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By giving people a reason to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.96,0:43:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,come back to the App Store every
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.06,0:43:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,day and giving the context of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.24,0:43:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,why we're making the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.83,0:43:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,recommendations that we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.47,0:43:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This redesign is more than just
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.91,0:43:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a facelift.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.71,0:43:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's created new opportunities
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.06,0:43:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to get discovered that haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.32,0:43:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,existed before.
