Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.60,0:43:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps and Games tabs, which give
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.28,0:43:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,focus to each of those areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.81,0:43:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But as always, you shouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.71,0:43:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,just rely on being featured by
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.04,0:43:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the App Store to improve your
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.78,0:43:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,app discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.27,0:43:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's things you can do even
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.80,0:43:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,starting now to get ready for
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.83,0:43:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the new App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.31,0:43:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to talk just a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.00,0:43:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,couple minutes about them.
