Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.26,0:44:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that we announced last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.26,0:44:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,giving you brand new
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.61,0:44:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunities for creating
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.63,0:44:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,sustainable businesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.87,0:44:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll want to start thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.29,0:44:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,now about the title of these
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.06,0:44:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in-app purchases and the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.01,0:44:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,description and the image that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.75,0:44:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to use for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.27,0:44:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly now that they have
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.35,0:44:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,such increased visibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.63,0:44:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a couple of StoreKit
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.89,0:44:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sessions and an iTunes Connect
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.04,0:44:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,session where you can get more
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.87,0:44:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,information about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.98,0:44:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll review those at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.91,0:44:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Titles are now 30 characters in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.44,0:44:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the App Store, in the all new
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.52,0:44:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.86,0:44:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But in addition, you will have a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.88,0:44:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,subtitle.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.68,0:44:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Monika showed this in context as
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.29,0:44:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.18,0:44:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll want to think carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.28,0:44:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,about how to use this subtitle
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.58,0:44:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to convey what your app does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.89,0:44:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To give a little bit more
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.86,0:44:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,information about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.72,0:44:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To say something compelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.13,0:44:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't be misleading.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.54,0:44:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider using your subtitle to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.24,0:44:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,highlight a feature or a typical
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.88,0:45:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,use of your app that'll resonate
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.97,0:45:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with your audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.69,0:45:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And this subtitle will follow
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.95,0:45:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,your app title around throughout
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.28,0:45:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the app store, whether it's in
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.78,0:45:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the Apps or the Games tab, on a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.05,0:45:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,product page or in search
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.23,0:45:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,results.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.29,0:45:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about video app
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.60,0:45:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,previews.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.40,0:45:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that when customers
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.53,0:45:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,engage with these video app
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.73,0:45:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,previews, customers tend to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.99,0:45:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,download that app or game more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.26,0:45:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we thought about, "Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.32,0:45:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,how can we make it more obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.88,0:45:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that these are videos?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.80,0:45:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, auto-playing is one way
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.89,0:45:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.60,0:45:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we really encourage you,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.30,0:45:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly now that you can
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.21,0:45:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,have three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.25,0:45:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And they can be localized.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.64,0:45:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should really be thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.52,0:45:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,about how to create a video that
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.24,0:45:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,encourages customers to download
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.28,0:45:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,your app or game.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.60,0:45:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We think video is a big deal on
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.91,0:45:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.04,0:45:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can learn more about what
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.83,0:45:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,makes a compelling video by
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.95,0:45:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,visiting the site, and by
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.47,0:45:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,visiting the App Store labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.27,0:46:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in addition to your app
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.25,0:46:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,description, you can have 170
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.70,0:46:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,characters of text, which can be
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.17,0:46:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,updated any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.93,0:46:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We call this Promo Text.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.75,0:46:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This will get concatenated on
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.84,0:46:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,top of your app description.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.29,0:46:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it won't require an app
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.38,0:46:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,update.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.58,0:46:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a great way to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.71,0:46:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,about one of the new features
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.65,0:46:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a temporary feature or a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.90,0:46:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,price promotion that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.90,0:46:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,having or some new accolade that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.57,0:46:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,your app has received.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.36,0:46:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something else that you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.22,0:46:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,can start thinking about right
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.22,0:46:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.42,0:46:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about ratings and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.60,0:46:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,reviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.86,0:46:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This got some applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.83,0:46:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This warms my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.66,0:46:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We did a couple things in iOS
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.86,0:46:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,10.3 releasing a Reviews API.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.12,0:46:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And allowing developers to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.73,0:46:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,respond to reviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.75,0:46:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the response has been
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.91,0:46:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.26,0:46:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen almost 400,000 --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.92,0:46:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,this number's actually a little
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.17,0:46:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,old.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.09,0:46:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen almost 400,000
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.89,0:46:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,responses to reviews since the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.05,0:46:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,launch of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.51,0:46:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know that when customers
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.71,0:47:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,go back and change their rating
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.11,0:47:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,based on a response that they
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.63,0:47:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,have received from a developer,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.33,0:47:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,overwhelmingly that change in
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.15,0:47:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,direction is in a positive way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.42,0:47:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.30,0:47:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the new App Store, as Monika
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.74,0:47:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,mentioned, we no longer reset
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.03,0:47:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,app rating when you submit a new
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.22,0:47:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,version.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.83,0:47:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is awesome for many
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.96,0:47:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,developers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.46,0:47:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Some developers wouldn't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.31,0:47:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,resetting that rating.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.20,0:47:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, with the new App Store,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.28,0:47:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with each submission you're
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.24,0:47:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,going to have the ability to do
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.33,0:47:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so, to reset your rating.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.46,0:47:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should be careful about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.41,0:47:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.58,0:47:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like an interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.28,0:47:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,option.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.72,0:47:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But we know that customers value
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.81,0:47:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that rating or seeing that an
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.73,0:47:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,app has ratings, a lot, when
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.47,0:47:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they're making a download
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.17,0:47:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.53,0:47:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you will want to be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.96,0:47:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.89,0:47:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get advice about best
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.46,0:47:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,practices associated with
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.34,0:47:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,responding to customer reviews
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.71,0:47:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by visiting this URL.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.36,0:47:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And like we mentioned, we
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.58,0:47:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,strongly recommend you make
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.94,0:48:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,responding to customer reviews a
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.83,0:48:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,regular part of your customer
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.85,0:48:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,service hygiene.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.43,0:48:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And in fact, in July, in iTunes
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.40,0:48:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Connect, we'll be enabling a new
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.36,0:48:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,role in iTunes Connect for
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.91,0:48:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,customer service so that you can
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.82,0:48:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have somebody that's focused
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.02,0:48:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,just on that and doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.94,0:48:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,access to other elements inside
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.61,0:48:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.58,0:48:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're constantly improving the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.67,0:48:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,way Core Search works in the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.78,0:48:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.61,0:48:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But the most visible thing we've
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.77,0:48:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,done this year is by adding the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.26,0:48:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,stories that our editors are
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.45,0:48:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.42,0:48:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, in-app purchases,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.96,0:48:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,categories and developers will
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.01,0:48:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to appear in these
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.19,0:48:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,search results as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.44,0:48:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of search, last year we
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.99,0:48:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,announced Search Ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.05,0:48:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it launched in the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.74,0:48:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it launched in the UK,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.72,0:48:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Australia and New Zealand in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.74,0:48:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,April.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.43,0:48:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The results have been really
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.61,0:48:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,strong for advertisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.32,0:48:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,High tap through rates.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.26,0:48:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversion rates above 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.46,0:48:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And cost per acquisition just
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.81,0:48:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,over a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.41,0:48:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,These are really impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.87,0:49:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,numbers for those that know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.27,0:49:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,stuff about advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.61,0:49:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An apps flyer industry study
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.44,0:49:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,published earlier this year
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.07,0:49:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,described the quality of users
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.56,0:49:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Search Ads delivers were the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.89,0:49:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,best 30-day retention rate for
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.68,0:49:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,iOS apps and a top three ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.93,0:49:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for games.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.44,0:49:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're working hard to deliver
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.60,0:49:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunities to drive downloads
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.84,0:49:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and engagement with your apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.89,0:49:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And bringing Search Ads to more
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.32,0:49:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the markets that you've told
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.15,0:49:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,us are important to your
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.97,0:49:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,business.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.96,0:49:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Many developers large and small
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.42,0:49:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,have already taken advantage of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.48,0:49:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.60,0:49:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is another thing you'll
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.60,0:49:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,want to consult with us about to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.03,0:49:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,find out if it's right for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.88,0:49:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In summary, there's plenty for
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.56,0:49:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you to be thinking about even
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.77,0:49:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,now in advance of iOS 11
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.44,0:49:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,shipping as it relates to your
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.97,0:49:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,app's presence in the Apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.98,0:49:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And we hope you take advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.02,0:49:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of the folks that are here from
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.02,0:49:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the App Store this week to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.63,0:49:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,more about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.65,0:49:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For more information on this
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.83,0:49:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,session you can visit this site.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.57,0:49:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are related sessions
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.64,0:49:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,listed as well as labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.12,0:49:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come speak with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.84,0:50:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Last thing I want to say is that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.15,0:50:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it was my honor to be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.27,0:50:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,introduce this new App Store
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.45,0:50:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that's been a few years in the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.70,0:50:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,running.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.12,0:50:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was done with a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.91,0:50:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,cross-functional work.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.26,0:50:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know some of those folks in
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.27,0:50:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the audience today.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.72,0:50:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Those that work in the App Store
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.87,0:50:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,please stand up for a second to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.91,0:50:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,get recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.17,0:50:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up for these folks who
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.07,0:50:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,have been working their butts
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.82,0:50:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,off.
